roup\" style=\"width:1%\">relating to the <a href=\"/wiki/European_Union\" title=\"European Union\">European Union</a> (formally <a href=\"/wiki/European_Communities\" title=\"European Communities\">European Communities</a>)</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Acts_of_Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom_relating_to_the_European_Communities_and_the_European_Union\" title=\"Acts of Parliament of the United Kingdom relating to the European Communities and the European Union\">1972 to date</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Church_of_England\" title=\"Church of England\">Church of England</a> measures</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Church_of_England_Measures\" title=\"List of Church of England Measures\">List</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Church_of_England_Assembly_(Powers)_Act_1919\" title=\"Church of England Assembly (Powers) Act 1919\">Church of England Assembly (Powers) Act 1919</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Legislation of <a href=\"/wiki/Devolution\" title=\"Devolution\">devolved</a> institutions</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Act_of_the_Scottish_Parliament\" title=\"Act of the Scottish Parliament\">Acts of the Scottish Parliament</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Acts_of_the_Scottish_Parliament_from_1999\" title=\"List of Acts of the Scottish Parliament from 1999\">List</a></li></ul></l